<bibRefCitation box="[734,954,1917,1942]" pageId="3" pageNumber="445" refId="ref2860" refString="Viraktamath, C. A. (2011) Revision of the Oriental and Australian Agalliini (Hemiptera: Cicadellidae: Megophthalminae). Zootaxa, 2844, 1 - 118." type="journal article">Viraktamath (2011)</bibRefCitation>
